<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Special Surprise</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #fae1dd;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            cursor: pointer;
            position: relative;
        }

        .envelope {
            position: relative;
            width: 300px;
            height: 200px;
            background-color: #f08080;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .envelope::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 2;
            border-left: 150px solid transparent;
            border-right: 150px solid transparent;
            border-top: 100px solid #f4978e;
            transition: transform 0.5s;
            transform-origin: top;
        }

        .letter {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 80%;
            height: 80%;
            background: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: 0.5s;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .container:hover .envelope::before {
            transform: rotateX(180deg);
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .container:hover .letter {
            bottom: 100px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        h2 { font-size: 18px; color: #d00000; }
        p { font-size: 14px; color: #333; }
        .heart { color: #d00000; font-size: 24px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="envelope"></div>
    <div class="letter">
        <div class="heart">❤️</div>
        <h2>Untuk Istriku Tersayang</h2>
        <p>Terima kasih sudah selalu ada di sampingku. Kamu adalah hal terbaik yang pernah terjadi dalam hidupku.</p>
        <p><strong>I Love You!</strong></p>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
